icals  (2015):[4] "Product Information. Symdeko (ivacaftor-tezacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals  (2022):[5] "Product Information. Trikafta (elexacaftor/ivacaftor/tezacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals  (2019):', 1767363028);
